Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:28.47,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\fscx90\fscy90}わたしは Queen of the Night
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.98,0:22:13.81,ED_CH,,0,0,48,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\fscx90\fscy90}为了记住今天发生的事情
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.48,0:22:18.69,ED_CH,,0,0,48,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\fscx90\fscy90}我要一字一句写进日记
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.98,0:22:22.36,ED_CH,,0,0,48,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\fscx90\fscy90}无论开心还是不开心的事
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.36,0:22:26.87,ED_CH,,0,0,48,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\fscx90\fscy90}人生只有一次所以都要记住
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.08,0:22:31.33,ED_CH,,0,0,48,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\fscx90\fscy90}重要的东西通常都是
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.54,0:22:34.71,ED_CH,,0,0,48,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\fscx90\fscy90}失去之后才会意识到
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.83,0:22:47.89,ED_CH,,0,0,48,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\fscx90\fscy90}所有一切都是为了迎来完美结局才开始的
