Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.02,0:22:58.27,ED_CH,,0,0,48,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\fscx90\fscy90}我更想再亲自去尝试一次
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.44,0:23:04.03,ED_CH,,0,0,48,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\fscx90\fscy90}甜蜜的月亮 比起闪闪发光的宝石
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.03,0:23:08.28,ED_CH,,0,0,48,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\fscx90\fscy90}我选择灌满砂糖的甜蜜幸福
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.58,0:23:15.33,ED_CH,,0,0,48,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\fscx90\fscy90}和碧蓝清净的未来 一定会抓住
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.33,0:23:21.09,ED_CH,,0,0,48,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\fscx90\fscy90}夜之女王
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.01,0:23:28.47,ED_CH,,0,0,48,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\fscx90\fscy90}我就是夜之女王
